1. *Drugom* stranom sveta dolazim do novih otkrića. (I reach to new findings on the other side of the world.) 
2. On je bio s druge *drugom* strane ulice. (He was on the other side of the street.)
3. Čudna sudbina oduvek je menjala putanju moje života u *drugom* pravcu. (A strange fate always changed the course of my life in a different direction.) 
4. *Drugom* prilikom ću ti ispričati svoju priču. (I'll tell you my story another time.) 
5. Osećam da je njegov pogled usmeren u *drugom* smeru. (I feel that his gaze is directed in a different direction.)